title: Episode 32 w/ Combat Jack and Jack Thriller
itunes:title: Episode 32 w/ Combat Jack and Jack Thriller
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Combat Jack of the Combat Jack show and comedian Jack Thriller. They discuss the current state of hip hop podcast, podcast beefs, and hip hop in general. In what might be the longest Drink Champs episode to date the guys drink, laugh and also have some tense moments. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
